{"tid":1561014,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"消防傷病者分流","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T13:27:53.000Z","uid":266780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ca174827a0f42c25eea4d17315fb3d1933fff6da","tid":1561014,"uid":266780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VnrHGoL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnrHGoL.png&h=268b88cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www3.ha.org.hk/haconvention/hac2013/proceedings/downloads/PS1.1.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww3.ha.org.hk%2Fhaconvention%2Fhac2013%2Fproceedings%2Fdownloads%2FPS1.1.pdf&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=f1872c81\" target=\"_blank\">http://www3.ha.org.hk/haconvention/hac2013/proceedings/downloads/PS1.1.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nFSD做分流, 唔係流架,<br />\n<br />\n最基本, 要分佢係咪死左 (無呼吸, 無脈搏)/身首異處--&gt;黑牌, 最後送走<br />\n會行會走會叫, 自己行去綠地蓆坐低--&gt;綠牌, 等紅黃牌走後才走<br />\n無即時生命危險, 但行唔到, 例如小腿骨折/手骨折---&gt;黃牌, 等紅牌走後立即走<br />\n未死, 但有即時生命危險, 例如大量出血, 人事不醒(有呼吸脈搏), 內出血(爆肝/血胸), 雙大腿骨折(車禍)--&gt;紅牌, 如有人手, 要KEEP住睇實佢, TAKE RECORD, 第一優先送院.<br />\n<br />\n即係分得紅牌, 一定會做初步檢查(即係你地學FA時的全身檢查, 由頭摸到腳趾尾), 一定知傷勢的, 不會用眼望吓就算(除非HEA做), 否則分不到流, 最少分不到死還是人事不醒.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁又點會6個紅牌變咗得番3個?<br />\n</span><br />\n除非都變了黑牌."},{"pid":"1ce09f53e3a72b2a411e6144173a963ea4b14088","tid":1561014,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"819a2c13613dc1155e2d687cf0211c0f0befd030","tid":1561014,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[多圖高清] [不廢up] 一人一文宣行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560411</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}